{"type":null,"faqId":35593,"title":"如何清洗手环？","answer":"您可以用沾水的纸巾或湿布清洁手环，然后使用干布或干纸巾彻底擦干。清洁过程中需要注意以下几点：\n1.请勿添加化学洗涤用品。\n2.蓝牙耳机与腕带分开单独清洁，切勿长时间浸泡。\n3.请留意MIC孔和耳机孔是否有水珠残留，残留水珠可能影响耳机通话质量，您可以用纸巾吸干水珠。","faqTypeId":212,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":1,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"373","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1437124654000,"seriesProductName":"B1-Honor","visitedTimes":267,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"荣耀手环,B1,清洗,洗,清洁","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}